{"id":634527,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/【敏感瓷】你听明白了吗？/","date":"2020-02-06T17:57:36Z","modified":"2020-02-06T20:17:57Z","title":"【敏感瓷】“你听明白了吗？”","content":"<p>新浪微博网友：“你听明白了吗？”已成为违禁词。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-634532\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/Image-from-iOS-3-1-728x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"1024\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/Image-from-iOS-3-1-728x1024.jpg 728w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/Image-from-iOS-3-1-213x300.jpg 213w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/Image-from-iOS-3-1-768x1080.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/Image-from-iOS-3-1.jpg 828w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\" /></p>\n<p>我们希望你冷静下来好好反思，并郑重告诫你：如果你固执己见，不思悔改，继续进行违法活动，你将会受到法律的制裁！你听明白了吗？</p>\n<p>答：明白。</p>\n<p>——武汉市公安局武昌分局中南路街派出所训诫书 被训诫者：李文亮 训诫者：胡桂芳 徐金杭（2020年1月3日）</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634601\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-4.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-4-212x300.jpg 212w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-4-724x1024.jpg 724w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/1-4-768x1087.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n","author":970,"categories":[18271,38912,16848,15868],"tags":[39755,28517,39753]}